  <http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/>
XSL Transformations (XSLT) :
  <http://www.w3.org/TR/xslt>
XML Path Language (XPath) :
  <http://www.w3.org/TR/xpath>
Extensible Markup Language (XML) 1.0 :
  <http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-xml>

